    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156360/extras/c0d88f942f7a61fa56724d9b3cde5413.poster.avif?t=1749999505\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156360/extras/c0d88f942f7a61fa56724d9b3cde5413.webm?t=1749999505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156360/extras/c0d88f942f7a61fa56724d9b3cde5413.mp4?t=1749999505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Dominate the Universe</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roam the galaxy destroying enemy ships, running into special events and shopping at Galactic Bazaars for upgrades to your ship in this roguelite space adventure! Roll your Crew dice and use your wits to keep your ships system maintained as you battle for your life.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Manage Your Fate</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How you deal with the rolls of your Crew dice is the decider between life and death. Make the wrong move and you can pay dearly for it! Make the right ones and you'll earn your victory!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156360/extras/383f7734e6f590f8bfbb4ac04c6f9b3a.poster.avif?t=1749999505\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156360/extras/383f7734e6f590f8bfbb4ac04c6f9b3a.webm?t=1749999505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156360/extras/383f7734e6f590f8bfbb4ac04c6f9b3a.mp4?t=1749999505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Upgrade Your Chances</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn upgrades (or disasters!) through special events, or by shopping at the Galactic Bazaar. Specialise your Crew die into specific ship systems to earn extra bonuses from their placement, or even upgrade them to Wildcards which fit all system dice! How you equip your ship will determine whether you come out alive, or whether you suffocate in the cold expanse of space!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156360/extras/8cd1b989b0eb4b806bd8db20e33710b3.poster.avif?t=1749999505\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156360/extras/8cd1b989b0eb4b806bd8db20e33710b3.webm?t=1749999505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156360/extras/8cd1b989b0eb4b806bd8db20e33710b3.mp4?t=1749999505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Unlock Ships</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn experience through your runs and unlock new ships to play with! Each ship has its strengths and weaknesses. Pick the right one for your playstyle to succeed!</p></li></ul>",
